- cs.TL (Type Theory) is another possible category as the paper uses intersection and product types in its type system. 
- cs.LG (Language and Automata Theory) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper deals with the semantics of a logical system. 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the least likely category, but still possible as the paper deals with the semantics of a language.
